description: OPEN HOUSE CANCELLED - OFFER ACCEPTED!! Unit 2E @ The Ceinture boasts a wide open floor plan that flows effortlessly into 2 bedrooms, 2 full baths, & a home office that can easily be used as 3rd bedroom. A unique layout with 1,548 sq ft of luxury finishes & a DEEDED garage parking spot! The Ceinture offers 4,000 sq ft of luxe amenities including a MASSIVE ROOF DECK w/ several seating areas, gas grills, STUNNING 360° City Views & a Sky Clubroom. Modern/digital-entry lobby w/ elevator & concierge, fitness center, and work-café. Unit highlights: Chef’s kitchen w/ BOSCH appliances, custom cabinetry w/ under cabinet lighting, quartz countertops & waterfall peninsula. Gleaming HW floors & LUTRON controlled recessed lighting. Built-in SONOS surround sound, high ceilings & large windows. Primary en-suite BR has spacious walk-in closet & XL spa-like bathroom w/ GROHE fixtures. In-unit washer/dryer. LARGE closets. Conveniently located 0.4 miles from Broadway T stop. This unit won't last long...
